{"tid":879202,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"90後必備童年漫畫","createTime":"2018-10-27T17:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T02:11:14.000Z","uid":139613,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93a0429bcf17235dacd67238aa070171dcee42d2","tid":879202,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"老夫子一定唔少得<br />\n20蚊其實對嗰時嘅自己係貴所以有錢先買<br />\n<br />\n其次仲有爆笑王 10蚊本 又有粗口又抵死<br />\n可惜後來一直加價<br />\n<br />\n仲有黑貓白貓 呢啲又講歷史 又有劇情 小知識嘅有益書刊<br />\n<br />\n以為每一個星期都有好書睇<br />\n而家真係買少見少 都唔見更新了<br />\n儲齊一套嘅滿足感真係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問自己好彩唔係出生係玩抖音嘅年代"},{"pid":"bcd2e03a6cdbea6a6201a9236aeb81a980dc43cd","tid":879202,"uid":202409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T17:57:00.000Z","msg":"通靈王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5cc2ec0a230ad50bb9e50bbdb645b96da6dd36","tid":879202,"uid":54283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"數碼暴龍01"},{"pid":"771df69670324e8aa293b6248a7271c7612af63a","tid":879202,"uid":204571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"HunterXHunter<br />\n狐忍<br />\n貯金大冒險"},{"pid":"c4b74fda885007dea350175a374a016646eefa81","tid":879202,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"漢堡拳"}]}